1
00:00:30,750 --> 00:00:32,708
Pak cik, kamu semua buat apa?

2
00:00:33,333 --> 00:00:35,166
Teratai boleh ubati kecederaan fizikal.

3
00:00:35,250 --> 00:00:38,375
Putera Mahkota Ketiga potong tubuhnya
untuk balas jasa ibu bapanya.

4
00:00:38,458 --> 00:00:42,083
Kemudian gurunya pulihkan tubuhnya
dengan batang dan akar teratai.

5
00:00:42,166 --> 00:00:44,125
Berapa banyak kad ajaib dia guna?

6
00:00:44,208 --> 00:00:46,416
Entah. Seluruh tempat itu terbakar.

7
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:50,250
Kesan sampingan
Tembok Api Suci 9 Naga paling kuat.

8
00:00:50,333 --> 00:00:51,666
Bila dia akan sedar?

9
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:54,000
Jangan risau. Dia takkan mati.

10
00:01:19,416 --> 00:01:23,041
AGENT FROM ABOVE

11
00:01:23,541 --> 00:01:27,833
TERJERUMUS KE JURANG GELAP

12
00:01:45,291 --> 00:01:46,583
Sayang, jangan pergi.

13
00:01:58,166 --> 00:01:59,000
Han Chieh.

14
00:02:00,083 --> 00:02:01,250
Awak dah sedar?

15
00:02:01,750 --> 00:02:03,541
Bagaimana keadaan awak?

16
00:02:18,416 --> 00:02:21,375
Betulkah awak nak selesaikan
banyak kes serentak?

17
00:02:21,458 --> 00:02:23,333
Pergi matilah, saya tak peduli.

18
00:02:23,416 --> 00:02:25,000
Han Chieh, apa awak buat?

19
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:28,750
RAJA SYAITAN HASUT SEORANG LELAKI

20
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:31,000
Bukankah awak kata
Raja Syaitan ada ejen baru?

21
00:02:31,083 --> 00:02:34,000
- Awak tak tahu pun tentang dia.
- Tak kisahlah.

22
00:02:34,583 --> 00:02:37,666
Jika bedebah itu dibiarkan,
bertambah lagilah mangsa.

23
00:02:38,166 --> 00:02:39,708
CHIEH

24
00:02:42,041 --> 00:02:43,250
Puas hati?

25
00:02:43,833 --> 00:02:44,791
Hei.

26
00:02:45,625 --> 00:02:46,625
Hei!

27
00:02:57,250 --> 00:03:01,125
"Pergi ke puncak Gunung Buddha
untuk menguatkan badan."

28
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:04,875
Gunung Buddha?

29
00:03:07,458 --> 00:03:08,666
Chen Chi-sha.

30
00:03:10,666 --> 00:03:11,500
Penat sial.

31
00:03:11,583 --> 00:03:12,583
BUDDHA

32
00:03:12,666 --> 00:03:14,375
Lepas kalahkan Chen Chi-sha,

33
00:03:14,458 --> 00:03:17,958
saya simpan semua senjata sihirnya
di dalam peti besi.

34
00:03:35,166 --> 00:03:36,416
Berhenti guna sihir.

35
00:03:37,083 --> 00:03:41,458
Bersaralah. Saya akan lindungi awak
daripada syaitan dan hantu.

36
00:03:43,666 --> 00:03:45,875
Awak ingat awak tak boleh dikalahkan?

37
00:03:56,041 --> 00:03:57,708
Awak bertuah kali ini.

38
00:03:58,916 --> 00:04:02,833
Jika Raja Syaitan dapat capai
kuasa penuh, matilah awak.

39
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:13,625
Peti besi itu macam tak ada
benda baik langsung.

40
00:04:13,708 --> 00:04:15,458
Betulkah Putera tak kenakan awak?

41
00:04:15,541 --> 00:04:17,458
Dia hantar mesej kepada saya.

42
00:04:17,541 --> 00:04:19,916
Jika gaduh pun, dia takkan kenakan saya.

43
00:04:20,625 --> 00:04:24,458
Sebenarnya, awak yang kenakan saya.
Kenapa kita tak sampai-sampai?

44
00:04:29,041 --> 00:04:30,041
Hei.

45
00:04:31,875 --> 00:04:32,958
Awak ada kuncinya?

46
00:04:52,708 --> 00:04:53,958
Terkejut aku.

47
00:04:55,541 --> 00:04:58,750
SIFAR, SATU, DUA, TIGA, EMPAT,
LIMA, ENAM, TUJUH, LAPAN, SEMBILAN

48
00:04:58,833 --> 00:05:00,708
Alamak, ini apa benda?

49
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,833
Biar benar.

50
00:06:00,666 --> 00:06:01,791
Mak kau!

51
00:06:03,833 --> 00:06:04,708
Apa ini?

52
00:06:16,541 --> 00:06:18,000
Ayuh, gerak.

53
00:06:19,125 --> 00:06:20,250
Cepat.

54
00:06:24,625 --> 00:06:25,458
Abu colok.

55
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,125
Chen Chi-sha letak awak dalam kotak?

56
00:06:44,625 --> 00:06:45,750
Kenapa?

57
00:06:51,791 --> 00:06:52,875
Saya?

58
00:06:54,250 --> 00:06:55,916
Dia nak beritahu sesuatukah?

59
00:06:57,625 --> 00:06:58,458
Wu…

60
00:06:59,375 --> 00:07:00,541
Wu Tien-chi?

61
00:07:03,916 --> 00:07:06,916
Wu Meng-hsueh.

62
00:07:09,916 --> 00:07:11,500
Wu Meng-hsueh?

63
00:07:15,416 --> 00:07:19,541
- Siasat nama Wu Meng-hsueh.
- Saya ke balai dulu. Nanti saya beritahu.

64
00:07:19,625 --> 00:07:20,500
Okey.

65
00:07:23,583 --> 00:07:24,791
Sebelah kiri…

66
00:07:27,041 --> 00:07:28,333
Menyorok…

67
00:07:29,541 --> 00:07:31,166
Sudahlah.

68
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:33,791
Sudahlah, gerak…

69
00:07:34,375 --> 00:07:35,750
- Gerak.
- Wang Hsiao-ming.

70
00:07:36,791 --> 00:07:38,291
Siapa bayar bil Internet?

71
00:07:39,416 --> 00:07:40,958
Awas. Bom tangan!

72
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:42,166
Awak bayar.

73
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:43,541
Jaga-jaga!

74
00:07:43,625 --> 00:07:46,208
Jadilah abang dan jaga hantu kecil itu.

75
00:07:46,916 --> 00:07:48,208
- Apa?
- Apa?

76
00:07:48,291 --> 00:07:50,750
Okey, baiklah.

77
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:54,208
- Pergi dulu.
- Selamat jalan.

78
00:07:59,625 --> 00:08:00,666
Mari main.

79
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:07,750
Apa awak nak?

80
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:09,750
Saya nak kencing.

81
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,083
Saya nak kencing.

82
00:08:15,083 --> 00:08:17,125
Dia nak kencing. Macam mana?

83
00:08:17,791 --> 00:08:18,708
Hei!

84
00:08:20,375 --> 00:08:23,916
Wu Meng-hsueh itu nama lama Wu Tien-chi.
Dia kerja bidang kewangan.

85
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,458
Ada desas-desus kata

86
00:08:25,541 --> 00:08:28,833
dia boleh ramal naik turun saham
dan ramalannya tepat.

87
00:08:29,625 --> 00:08:32,083
Dia pernah membunuh semasa remaja.

88
00:08:36,041 --> 00:08:38,750
Chen Chi-sha kata
Wu Tien-chi ialah ejen baru,

89
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:40,791
manakala dia pula cuma boneka.

90
00:08:40,875 --> 00:08:45,125
Wang Yu-ching mungkin dengan Wu Tien-chi,
sebab Chen Chi-sha dah mati.

91
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:48,041
Apa dia nak buat?

92
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,958
En. Wang.

93
00:09:02,708 --> 00:09:06,083
Jika awak terus begini, nanti jatuh sakit.
Baliklah rehat.

94
00:09:06,166 --> 00:09:09,041
Kalau ada berita,
kami akan maklumkan segera.

95
00:09:09,958 --> 00:09:13,083
Tak apa. Saya nak tunggu Ching di sini.

96
00:09:13,833 --> 00:09:15,958
Lagipun, di rumah tak ada orang.

97
00:09:32,083 --> 00:09:33,000
Helo?

98
00:09:33,916 --> 00:09:35,583
Ini ayah Yu-ching?

99
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:37,500
Ya, saya.

100
00:09:38,041 --> 00:09:38,958
Saya kawan dia.

101
00:09:39,708 --> 00:09:43,291
Pernah dengar tentang
Yu-ching dibuli teruk di sekolah?

102
00:09:43,375 --> 00:09:47,708
Dia dibuli di sekolah?
Kenapa dia tak pernah cerita pula?

103
00:09:48,208 --> 00:09:49,333
Awak rakan sekelas?

104
00:09:49,416 --> 00:09:52,500
Saya tahu lokasi dia,
tapi saya tak nak cari masalah.

105
00:09:53,083 --> 00:09:56,750
Jadi, tolong janji satu perkara.
Jangan beritahu polis.

106
00:09:57,458 --> 00:10:00,916
- Itu saja cara saya boleh bantu.
- Okey, saya janji.

107
00:10:04,625 --> 00:10:05,500
FAIL JENAYAH

108
00:10:05,583 --> 00:10:08,458
Dulu sayalah pendakwa
dalam kes Wu Meng-hsueh.

109
00:10:09,208 --> 00:10:10,250
Dah 20 tahun.

110
00:10:10,333 --> 00:10:12,708
Tapi awak masih ingat kes ini, En. Chen.

111
00:10:13,375 --> 00:10:14,666
Mustahil boleh lupa.

112
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:18,416
Saya tak boleh terima keputusan
kes Wu Meng-hsueh.

113
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,708
HAKIM PENGERUSI: CHANG HO-CHENG

114
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:29,708
Kenapa?

115
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:35,291
- Sila teruskan.
- Ketika itu Wu Meng-hsueh 15 tahun.

116
00:10:36,083 --> 00:10:39,125
Mangsa pula gadis berusia 16 tahun.

117
00:10:39,958 --> 00:10:42,666
Dia mati bersama neneknya di rumah mereka.

118
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,791
- Apa motifnya?
- Jenayah nafsu.

119
00:10:45,875 --> 00:10:47,916
Ada kesan serangan seksual pada mangsa.

120
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:51,625
Wu Meng-hsueh kata mereka bercinta,
tapi nenek mangsa halang.

121
00:10:52,333 --> 00:10:55,166
Ayah Wu Meng-hsueh pula peguam terkenal

122
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:57,750
dan ada pasukan besar untuk bebaskan dia.

123
00:10:57,833 --> 00:11:01,458
Mereka guna kelemahan undang-undang
dengan alasan dia bawah umur.

124
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:06,083
Datuk mangsa selalu di mahkamah,
tapi tak boleh bercakap kerana strok.

125
00:11:07,125 --> 00:11:11,041
Ayah Wu juga guna pelbagai kenalan VIP
untuk desak hakim pengerusi.

126
00:11:11,625 --> 00:11:16,375
Akhirnya, dia terima hukuman ringan,
tapi saya tak boleh buat apa-apa.

127
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:21,041
Datuk mangsa tak nak makan minum
selepas keputusan diumumkan.

128
00:11:21,125 --> 00:11:22,666
Dia mati tak lama kemudian.

129
00:11:23,166 --> 00:11:26,000
Wu Meng-hsueh dipenjarakan tak lama.

130
00:11:26,583 --> 00:11:29,750
Dia dibebaskan pada usia 20-an.

131
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,958
Saya kecewa kerana gagal
cari keadilan bagi mangsa.

132
00:11:35,625 --> 00:11:37,458
Tapi saya lebih marah dunia.

133
00:11:38,041 --> 00:11:40,750
Orang ada kuasa dan pengaruh
selalu boleh terlepas.

134
00:11:47,666 --> 00:11:50,875
HAKIM PENGERUSI, CHANG HO-CHENG

135
00:11:57,375 --> 00:11:59,916
Saya ajak setiausaha ayah Wu
jumpa di sini.

136
00:12:03,791 --> 00:12:06,458
Awak nampak gelisah saja. Kenapa?

137
00:12:10,375 --> 00:12:13,625
Hakim pengerusi kes itu,
Chang Ho-cheng ialah ayah saya.

138
00:12:17,208 --> 00:12:19,833
Ayah saya jarang cerita tentang kerja.

139
00:12:20,333 --> 00:12:23,166
Semasa saya sekolah menengah,
dia alami kemurungan teruk.

140
00:12:23,250 --> 00:12:25,375
Tak lama kemudian dia mati.

141
00:12:25,958 --> 00:12:29,333
Beberapa hari sebelum mati,
dia asyik kata, "Maaflah."

142
00:12:29,416 --> 00:12:31,541
Hari ini barulah saya tahu sebabnya.

143
00:12:32,708 --> 00:12:36,208
Dia asyik dihantui keputusan kes itu
sehinggalah dia mati.

144
00:12:38,458 --> 00:12:42,125
Dewa pun buat silap, apatah lagi manusia.

145
00:12:45,458 --> 00:12:48,333
Saya nekad nak sumbat
bedebah itu ke penjara.

146
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:54,625
Penjara? Dia patut dihumban terus
ke neraka paling bawah, tingkat 18.

147
00:12:56,958 --> 00:12:58,041
Ke tingkat 100.

148
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:06,458
Pn. Liu, saya Chang Min.
Kita dah cakap di telefon.

149
00:13:06,541 --> 00:13:07,875
Ini rakan kerja saya.

150
00:13:08,458 --> 00:13:13,416
Saya nak tanya tentang anak En. Wu,
Wu Meng-hsueh.

151
00:13:23,208 --> 00:13:24,333
Pn. Liu.

152
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:33,916
Kamu nak tahu apa?

153
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,833
Selepas keluar penjara,
dia dapat identiti baru.

154
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:39,333
Dia ada sembunyi atau lari
daripada apa-apa?

155
00:13:39,416 --> 00:13:43,333
Keluarganya memang berpengaruh.
Kenapa dia belajar Teknik Wumeng?

156
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,125
Sebab…

157
00:13:49,041 --> 00:13:51,000
dia nampak datuk mangsa di penjara.

158
00:13:53,958 --> 00:13:54,958
Pergi.

159
00:13:55,041 --> 00:13:56,083
Berambus.

160
00:13:57,500 --> 00:14:00,125
Kau bunuh isteri dan cucu aku.

161
00:14:00,666 --> 00:14:03,000
Aku akan kacau kau sampai kau mati.

162
00:14:03,083 --> 00:14:06,083
Aku akan balas perbuatan kau
di Mahkamah Neraka!

163
00:14:08,583 --> 00:14:10,291
Aku nak lihat kau dihumban

164
00:14:10,375 --> 00:14:12,166
ke tingkat 18 neraka!

165
00:14:13,333 --> 00:14:17,166
Wu Meng-hsueh minta bantuan ayahnya,
jadi En. Wu carikan mahaguru

166
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:21,166
yang kurung roh itu dalam
perasap cendana berbentuk gunung

167
00:14:21,250 --> 00:14:23,416
dan menguncinya dengan tangkal.

168
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:27,000
Di mana perasap itu?

169
00:14:28,958 --> 00:14:29,958
Saya tak tahu.

170
00:14:30,916 --> 00:14:34,625
Tapi lepas Wu Meng-hsueh bebas,
dia mengembara serata dunia.

171
00:14:36,541 --> 00:14:38,083
Dia nak belajar cara

172
00:14:38,833 --> 00:14:42,833
untuk buat sesuka hati tanpa dihukum
di Alam Manusia dan neraka.

173
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:46,000
Dia belajar teknik dan ilmu sihir,

174
00:14:46,083 --> 00:14:49,208
termasuk yang paling jahat, Teknik Wumeng.

175
00:14:52,333 --> 00:14:53,750
Apa yang awak dah buat?

176
00:14:55,250 --> 00:14:59,500
Kita ada empat pesaing.
Semuanya terlibat dalam kemalangan.

177
00:14:59,583 --> 00:15:02,750
Jadi, untunglah kita.
Kenapa nak marah pula?

178
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:03,958
Meng-hsueh.

179
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:07,250
Jangan buat benda bukan-bukan lagi.

180
00:15:08,958 --> 00:15:10,208
Kalau awak teruskan…

181
00:15:12,791 --> 00:15:13,916
ayah ubah wasiat.

182
00:15:15,250 --> 00:15:17,791
Awak takkan dapat satu sen pun.

183
00:15:20,916 --> 00:15:22,166
Jika berani, buatlah.

184
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,666
Jika ayah ubah wasiat,

185
00:15:27,375 --> 00:15:29,041
mangsa kemalangan seterusnya

186
00:15:29,916 --> 00:15:31,250
mungkin ayah.

187
00:15:31,875 --> 00:15:32,750
Awak…

188
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:35,875
Menyesal ayah tak biar awak
kena hukuman berat!

189
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:48,041
En. Wu tutup firma guaman itu.

190
00:15:49,875 --> 00:15:51,916
Saya berhenti kerja selepas dia bersara.

191
00:15:52,708 --> 00:15:54,875
Saya tak dengar berita mereka lagi.

192
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:08,875
- Mari cari perasap itu.
- Kenapa?

193
00:16:10,333 --> 00:16:12,333
Dia cuma takut satu saja. Karma.

194
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,791
Dilaporkan ke Mahkamah Neraka.

195
00:16:15,833 --> 00:16:19,250
Maksud awak, jika datuk mangsa
laporkan dia kepada Yama,

196
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:22,958
dia akan dihukum atas jenayahnya
selepas mati?

197
00:16:23,583 --> 00:16:26,333
Ya. Awak tahu cara nak cari
lokasi perasap itu?

198
00:16:27,541 --> 00:16:29,791
Saya minta balai dapatkan maklumatnya.

199
00:16:29,875 --> 00:16:31,208
Dia ada pasport asing.

200
00:16:31,291 --> 00:16:34,000
Asetnya dalam syarikat luar negara.
Ia akan ambil masa.

201
00:16:36,083 --> 00:16:40,500
Pandai Raja Syaitan pilih ejen.
Dia licik dan bijak.

202
00:16:41,083 --> 00:16:43,708
Bijak pun tak guna
jika cuma tahu buat jahat.

203
00:16:43,791 --> 00:16:45,791
Awak bodoh, tapi lebih baik daripada dia.

204
00:16:46,291 --> 00:16:47,958
Awak yang bodoh.

205
00:16:48,041 --> 00:16:49,291
Sensitif betul.

206
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:53,875
PASUKAN SIASATAN SATU

207
00:16:53,958 --> 00:16:55,666
- Tak guna!
- Bertenang.

208
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,166
Mana anak saya?

209
00:16:57,666 --> 00:16:58,833
Mana anak saya?

210
00:17:03,375 --> 00:17:04,208
Syabas.

211
00:17:06,625 --> 00:17:09,458
Lelaki yang dipukul itu penagih dadah,
Hsieh Kun-hao.

212
00:17:09,541 --> 00:17:12,916
Wang Cheng-nan dapat panggilan
yang kata penagih itu buli anaknya.

213
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:17,416
- Jadi dia syak penagih itu culik anaknya.
- Bagaimana Wang Cheng-nan cari dia?

214
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,291
Pemanggil itu beritahu lokasinya.

215
00:17:19,375 --> 00:17:22,708
Hsieh Kun-hao dipukul di rumah
yang Wu Tien-chi beli tiga tahun lalu,

216
00:17:22,791 --> 00:17:24,750
lokasi dia bunuh gadis dan nenek itu.

217
00:17:27,791 --> 00:17:30,208
Wu Tien-chi guna orang
untuk buat kerja kotor.

218
00:17:31,208 --> 00:17:32,250
Biasalah dia.

219
00:17:33,375 --> 00:17:35,458
Chao dah panggil dia ke balai.

220
00:17:38,125 --> 00:17:40,750
Saya beli apartmen itu lama dahulu.

221
00:17:40,833 --> 00:17:42,458
Dah lama ia kosong.

222
00:17:43,833 --> 00:17:46,000
Tak sangka ada orang pecah masuk.

223
00:17:46,583 --> 00:17:48,208
Kenapa awak beli rumah itu?

224
00:17:53,708 --> 00:17:57,041
Lokasinya bagus.
Nilainya akan meningkat nanti.

225
00:17:57,708 --> 00:17:59,916
Saya beli untuk tujuan pelaburan.

226
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:07,291
Nak tanya apa-apa lagi?

227
00:18:13,625 --> 00:18:15,250
- Terima kasih.
- Jaga diri.

228
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:22,041
- Kenapa biarkan dia pergi?
- Kita tak boleh tahan dia.

229
00:18:22,125 --> 00:18:26,083
Kita tiada bukti langsung
dia terlibat dalam kehilangan gadis itu.

230
00:18:26,166 --> 00:18:28,416
Nombor yang telefon Wang Cheng-nan

231
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:30,375
bukan nombor dalam negara ini.

232
00:18:30,458 --> 00:18:33,666
Jadi, kita tak dapat pastikan
dia yang guna nombor itu.

233
00:18:34,166 --> 00:18:35,250
Tapi…

234
00:18:35,333 --> 00:18:37,500
Pantau dia sepanjang masa.

235
00:18:39,166 --> 00:18:40,083
Baik.

236
00:18:48,958 --> 00:18:49,958
Helo.

237
00:18:51,375 --> 00:18:52,583
Jangan pura-puralah.

238
00:19:06,208 --> 00:19:07,583
Awak memang hebat.

239
00:19:08,333 --> 00:19:11,625
Awak lawan Chen Chi-sha tapi masih hidup.

240
00:19:14,125 --> 00:19:17,666
Beritahu Raja Syaitan,
saya tahu dia nak datang bermain.

241
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:21,666
Jika kamu nak main, saya pun nak.
Tapi lepaskan Wang Yu-ching dulu.

242
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:25,416
Syaratnya, jangan libatkan
orang tak bersalah.

243
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:30,291
Awak suka guna cara jahat, bukan?
Baiklah, mari kita lawan.

244
00:19:30,375 --> 00:19:33,791
Jika awak menang, awak boleh bunuh saya.

245
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,125
Bunyinya menarik.

246
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:47,916
Sayangnya, awak tak kenal saya.
Dengar baik-baik.

247
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:52,083
Sepanjang hidup saya,
saya paling benci peraturan.

248
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:55,375
Nampak tak orang di dalam?

249
00:19:56,041 --> 00:19:59,750
Mereka sentiasa tunduk
dan patuh peraturan,

250
00:20:00,916 --> 00:20:03,125
dan hidup sederhana.

251
00:20:03,833 --> 00:20:05,083
Untuk apa?

252
00:20:05,666 --> 00:20:06,791
Kebebasan.

253
00:20:07,791 --> 00:20:10,000
Tiada yang sehebat kebebasan.

254
00:20:15,625 --> 00:20:17,416
Saya dengar kad awak hebat.

255
00:20:20,541 --> 00:20:22,208
Saya tak sabar melihatnya.

256
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:43,458
Helo.

257
00:20:44,833 --> 00:20:45,958
Sila ikut sini.

258
00:20:46,583 --> 00:20:48,750
VIP dah sampai.

259
00:21:16,208 --> 00:21:18,708
Cuaca sejuk. Pakailah selimut malam-malam.

260
00:21:18,791 --> 00:21:20,166
Saya tahu.

261
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,541
Awak lupa ingatkan saya
tidur pakai stoking.

262
00:21:23,541 --> 00:21:24,916
- Pergi dulu.
- Okey.

263
00:21:53,958 --> 00:21:55,250
Kenapa datang balik?

264
00:22:00,375 --> 00:22:01,291
Leafy.

265
00:22:02,625 --> 00:22:03,958
Leafy.

266
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:06,375
Leafy.

267
00:22:21,166 --> 00:22:22,041
Terjun.

268
00:22:23,041 --> 00:22:24,166
Terjun.

269
00:22:25,083 --> 00:22:25,916
Terjun.

270
00:22:26,416 --> 00:22:27,625
Cepat terjun.

271
00:22:27,708 --> 00:22:28,708
Terjunlah.

272
00:22:28,791 --> 00:22:31,208
Celaka! Apa kau nak?

273
00:22:52,375 --> 00:22:53,250
Leafy.

274
00:22:54,041 --> 00:22:54,875
Leafy.

275
00:22:59,375 --> 00:23:00,375
Chieh.

276
00:23:56,583 --> 00:23:57,750
Apa awak nak?

277
00:23:58,333 --> 00:23:59,583
Sabar…

278
00:24:01,708 --> 00:24:06,000
Saya cuma hantar setiausaha comel saya
untuk periksa keadaan.

279
00:24:06,583 --> 00:24:08,416
Saya kasihankan Tuan Chen.

280
00:24:08,500 --> 00:24:12,166
Saya nak beri dia anak angkat.
Yeh Chih-ling sesuai tak?

281
00:24:14,125 --> 00:24:16,500
Jika awak kacau orang saya,
saya bunuh awak!

282
00:24:20,875 --> 00:24:22,791
Awak tak pernah bunuh orang, bukan?

283
00:24:25,375 --> 00:24:29,416
Awak bunuh banyak syaitan,
tapi bukan manusia yang hidup.

284
00:24:30,041 --> 00:24:31,333
Awak nak cuba?

285
00:24:32,916 --> 00:24:34,541
Awak nak tolak saya, bukan?

286
00:24:35,041 --> 00:24:37,208
Tengoklah. Kita sama.

287
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,125
Kita sama saja.

288
00:24:39,208 --> 00:24:41,416
- Chieh…
- Kita sama.

289
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:42,875
- Sabar, Chieh.
- Ayuh.

290
00:24:42,958 --> 00:24:44,125
Chieh.

291
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:48,458
Awak pandai buat orang marah.
Tapi cuma tahu cakap besar.

292
00:24:48,541 --> 00:24:52,625
Awak sendiri tak mampu buat.
Chen Chi-sha buat semua kerja kotor awak.

293
00:24:57,958 --> 00:25:00,791
Awak ingat polis macam awak hebat?

294
00:25:00,875 --> 00:25:05,000
Awak ingat unit awak yang tak cekap
dan korup mampu nak tangkap saya?

295
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:06,833
Kamu perlu mati dulu.

296
00:25:07,333 --> 00:25:09,875
Dah habis cakap? Itu tak cukup menghina.

297
00:25:10,458 --> 00:25:12,208
Provokasi awak lemah.

298
00:25:12,291 --> 00:25:14,916
Kenapa Raja Syaitan cari pengganti
yang lemah macam awak?

299
00:25:15,541 --> 00:25:17,083
Usaha lagi, okey?

300
00:25:22,458 --> 00:25:24,416
Chen Chi-sha cuma boneka.

301
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:27,791
Saya yang suruh dia bunuh orang.

302
00:25:27,875 --> 00:25:30,500
Orang tua itu tak setaraf
dengan saya, okey?

303
00:25:30,583 --> 00:25:31,916
Kamu semua tak guna.

304
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:35,875
Saya tahu undang-undang dan ilmu sihir.
Kamu nak main dengan saya?

305
00:25:35,958 --> 00:25:37,958
Saya mungkin bunuh Yeh Chih-ling dulu.

306
00:25:39,041 --> 00:25:40,750
Chieh, mari pergi.

307
00:25:40,833 --> 00:25:42,875
Chieh. Ayuh.

308
00:25:43,875 --> 00:25:45,375
Hei! Janganlah pergi!

309
00:25:53,458 --> 00:25:57,000
Sudah, bertenang.
Tak apa. Saya bukakan pintu.

310
00:25:57,916 --> 00:26:00,291
Masuk kereta. Jaga kepala.

311
00:26:00,375 --> 00:26:02,166
Duduk elok-elok.

312
00:26:05,291 --> 00:26:07,708
Gula darah rendah buat awak cepat marah.

313
00:26:27,333 --> 00:26:28,208
Chao.

314
00:26:28,791 --> 00:26:33,875
Han Chieh dah tolong kita
dapatkan waran geledah.

315
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,791
Nanti saya hantar.

316
00:26:44,208 --> 00:26:45,416
Apa yang kelakarnya?

317
00:26:50,416 --> 00:26:52,791
Chen Chi-sha cuma boneka.

318
00:26:52,875 --> 00:26:56,291
Saya yang suruh dia bunuh orang.

319
00:26:56,375 --> 00:26:57,375
Orang tua itu…

320
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:07,625
Pendakwa Chen benarkan
rumah Wu Tien-chi digeledah.

321
00:27:07,708 --> 00:27:09,083
Selain rakaman itu,

322
00:27:09,166 --> 00:27:13,125
orang di kelab malam nampak dia
masuk bilik peribadi dengan Chen Chi-sha.

323
00:27:28,208 --> 00:27:32,166
Perasap cendana yang bertangkal ini
disorok dengan baik.

324
00:27:32,250 --> 00:27:34,041
Inikah yang kamu cari?

325
00:27:39,541 --> 00:27:40,375
Ya.

326
00:27:40,875 --> 00:27:43,083
Chieh, ini bahan bukti.

327
00:27:43,583 --> 00:27:45,833
Jangan lupa pulangkan selepas selesai.

328
00:27:54,083 --> 00:27:56,750
Apa awak nak buat dengannya?

329
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:00,000
Saya akan simpan dulu

330
00:28:00,083 --> 00:28:02,958
dan bantu datuk mangsa
memohon Dekri Hitam.

331
00:28:06,583 --> 00:28:08,833
Akhirnya dia tersilap langkah.

332
00:28:08,916 --> 00:28:10,583
Mampuslah kau, Wu Tien-chi.

333
00:28:19,291 --> 00:28:21,166
PETA JALAN BANDAR TAIPEI

334
00:28:24,166 --> 00:28:25,750
Hei, saya tak fahamlah.

335
00:28:25,833 --> 00:28:28,958
Wu Tien-chi tipu Wang Cheng-nan
dan kata penagih itu suspek,

336
00:28:29,041 --> 00:28:31,916
malah sengaja pilih apartmen
tempat dia membunuh

337
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:33,375
sebagai tempat konflik.

338
00:28:33,458 --> 00:28:34,500
Apa muslihat dia?

339
00:28:35,958 --> 00:28:39,666
Tempat Wu Tien-chi membunuh.

340
00:28:41,875 --> 00:28:43,166
Matlamat Wu Tien-chi…

341
00:28:44,375 --> 00:28:45,791
Gadis itu tiada di sini.

342
00:28:45,875 --> 00:28:48,666
Ada kegunaan lain untuk Wang Yu-ching.

343
00:28:50,083 --> 00:28:51,458
Apartmen Wu Tien-chi.

344
00:28:52,500 --> 00:28:53,333
Dewan Heilung.

345
00:28:54,583 --> 00:28:56,041
Kes jiwa hakiki dicuri.

346
00:28:56,125 --> 00:28:58,291
TOKONG PAOAN, TOKONG LANTE, TOKONG FUHE

347
00:28:58,375 --> 00:29:01,333
Setiap lokasi ada
kes kematian aneh yang sama.

348
00:29:06,750 --> 00:29:08,541
Beri saya pen…

349
00:29:15,916 --> 00:29:17,375
DEWAN HEILUNG

350
00:29:22,875 --> 00:29:23,708
TOKONG FUHE

351
00:29:23,791 --> 00:29:24,958
TOKONG LANCHEN

352
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:26,583
TOKONG PAOAN

353
00:29:30,416 --> 00:29:31,666
Ini…

354
00:29:32,166 --> 00:29:33,291
Ini formasi sihir.

355
00:29:43,416 --> 00:29:44,791
Alamak.

356
00:29:46,041 --> 00:29:47,583
Saya terlepas pandang.

357
00:29:47,666 --> 00:29:49,625
Ketika Chen Chi-sha culik jiwa hakiki,

358
00:29:49,708 --> 00:29:51,708
Wu buat formasi sihir
dengan korban manusia

359
00:29:52,291 --> 00:29:55,708
untuk buka kunci supaya roh Raja Syaitan
boleh turun ke Alam Manusia.

360
00:30:02,708 --> 00:30:04,583
"Raja mayat akan dicipta.

361
00:30:04,666 --> 00:30:06,500
Bulan purnama bakal menjelma."

362
00:30:06,583 --> 00:30:07,416
Bulan purnama?

363
00:30:09,666 --> 00:30:11,583
Dulu pun semasa bulan purnama.

364
00:30:17,333 --> 00:30:19,041
Awak bertuah kali ini.

365
00:30:19,125 --> 00:30:22,083
Jika Raja Syaitan dapat capai
kuasa penuh, matilah awak.

366
00:30:23,166 --> 00:30:25,791
Bulan purnama,
formasi sihir, di tengah-tengah.

367
00:30:26,916 --> 00:30:30,125
Saya dah faham. Lima tahun lalu,
saya kalahkan dia secara kebetulan.

368
00:30:30,791 --> 00:30:33,625
Saya ganggu saat kemasukan Raja Syaitan.

369
00:30:34,583 --> 00:30:37,208
Formasi sihir yang lengkap
dapat salurkan rohnya,

370
00:30:37,291 --> 00:30:40,250
tapi dia tunggu tengah malam
semasa kedudukan bulan paling tinggi.

371
00:30:40,333 --> 00:30:43,458
Barulah dia capai
kuasa penuh melalui portal.

372
00:30:44,125 --> 00:30:48,041
Jika kau berani lengahkan aku,
aku akan heret kau ke neraka.

373
00:30:48,666 --> 00:30:49,875
Kali ini pun sama.

374
00:30:52,083 --> 00:30:53,583
WANG YU-CHING, DEWAN HEILUNG

375
00:30:54,125 --> 00:30:55,041
Mana portalnya?

376
00:30:57,875 --> 00:30:59,791
Di tengah-tengah formasi sihir,

377
00:31:00,958 --> 00:31:02,125
Pasar Dongfeng.

378
00:31:05,875 --> 00:31:08,958
Jadi, awak dan Pasar Dongfeng
jadi sasaran dari awal.

379
00:31:09,458 --> 00:31:11,041
Celaka, Wu Tien-chi.

380
00:31:16,875 --> 00:31:18,541
Tapi formasi itu belum siap.

381
00:31:19,708 --> 00:31:23,791
Korban di lokasi terakhir
mungkin Wang Yu-ching.

382
00:31:23,875 --> 00:31:25,625
PLAZA TASIK EMAS

383
00:31:26,208 --> 00:31:27,833
Kawal plaza ini dulu.

384
00:31:27,916 --> 00:31:30,833
Kelilingnya bangunan tinggi
dengan ribuan rumah.

385
00:31:30,916 --> 00:31:32,625
Dia boleh sorok di mana-mana.

386
00:31:38,625 --> 00:31:42,583
Mangsa dikorbankan dengan cara bunuh diri
atau dibunuh dengan mengerikan.

387
00:31:43,166 --> 00:31:44,625
Formasi sihir dapat kuasa gelap

388
00:31:44,708 --> 00:31:47,583
daripada ketakutan
dan kebencian mangsa sebelum mati.

389
00:31:49,958 --> 00:31:53,208
Wu Tien-chi simpan Wang Yu-ching
untuk dikorbankan.

390
00:31:53,291 --> 00:31:56,291
Tarikhnya tentu beberapa hari
sebelum bulan purnama.

391
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,208
Kita masih ada masa.

392
00:32:01,625 --> 00:32:05,500
PLAZA TASIK EMAS

393
00:33:15,208 --> 00:33:18,125
- Perjanjian kita masih sah, bukan?
- Lemah betul.

394
00:33:18,208 --> 00:33:21,708
Kau takut sangat orang tua itu
failkan aduan terhadap kau?

395
00:33:22,708 --> 00:33:24,916
Jika kau uruskan baik-baik,

396
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:28,083
walau apa pun yang kau buat
di Alam Manusia,

397
00:33:28,166 --> 00:33:31,875
Yama di Mahkamah Neraka pun
takkan boleh hukum kau

398
00:33:31,958 --> 00:33:35,333
selepas kau mati dan masuk neraka.

399
00:33:36,875 --> 00:33:41,000
Mana benda yang aku suruh buat?
Dah buat persiapan?

400
00:33:42,250 --> 00:33:43,541
Semuanya tersedia.

401
00:33:46,041 --> 00:33:47,541
Saya dah uji tadi.

402
00:33:49,166 --> 00:33:52,416
Chieh, Leafy dirasuk hantu wanita.

403
00:33:53,458 --> 00:33:54,458
Apa awak nak?

404
00:33:54,958 --> 00:33:57,166
Si bodoh itu ambil berat tentang dia.

405
00:34:00,666 --> 00:34:03,041
Jika kita letakkannya pada gadis itu

406
00:34:03,125 --> 00:34:04,875
dan Han Chieh jumpa pun,

407
00:34:04,958 --> 00:34:06,958
dia takkan berani bertindak gopoh.

408
00:34:14,208 --> 00:34:17,291
Jangan pandang rendah pada budak itu.

409
00:34:17,375 --> 00:34:20,666
Dia berjaya hapuskan Chen Chi-sha.

410
00:34:21,166 --> 00:34:23,416
Hati-hati.

411
00:34:24,291 --> 00:34:26,375
Ini fasa terakhir.

412
00:34:26,875 --> 00:34:28,833
Sempurnakan raja mayat dulu.

413
00:34:28,916 --> 00:34:32,666
Cari jalan untuk habiskan
senjata ajaibnya.

414
00:40:35,958 --> 00:40:37,666
Terjemahan sari kata oleh MMA

